  <accessibleRooms><![CDATA[<p>Access to the hotel is at street level with no steps. Standard rooms are accessible to persons of reduced mobility, there are adapted rooms which are wheelchair accessible with a lower bathroom sink, a toilet with rails. There is a wheelchair accessible lift in the property which serves all floors.</p>
<p>Please give our Reservations team a call if you would like to book an adapted room, so we can ensure this is the right property for you.</p>
<p> </p>]]></accessibleRooms>
